title: Parquet Courts - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Parquet Courts performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded April 22, 2022.

Songs:
Watching Strangers Smile
Walking At A Downtown Pace
Plant Life
Homo Sapien

Andrew Savage - Vocals / Guitar / Keyboard

Max Savage - Drums / Vocals
Doug Marvin - Percussion

Host: Troy Nelson
